{"tid":1824600,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界根本冇嘢係公平","createTime":"2020-01-14T14:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T04:20:06.000Z","uid":81190,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ac99a1a6357c297364e112965c2e9e11d08a7c07","tid":1824600,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"除咗有冇錢之外，更重要嘅係智力<br />\n讀緊書要智力嚟幫手記嘢思考，返工聰明嘅話諗到更快嘅方法解決問題，幫到公司手自然升職升得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真，生得聰明嘅話都容易啲溝到女<br />\n<br />\n生得聰明根本就玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a559a743e87e2cc0d164fbc7c9b55f21fbf5893a","tid":1824600,"uid":81190,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"如果靠努力就可以改變到好似神人咁，咁呢個世界冇廢人啦"},{"pid":"edbeda773f0040ca2696ae995f04f685a8bb5cb3","tid":1824600,"uid":313072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:46:37.000Z","msg":"你依家先知？"},{"pid":"2a36ea138acb3ddcca49f2204fd175fb7b1cb51c","tid":1824600,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4145e0deeb0cbec7c86447c7d8700291869a06e4","tid":1824600,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"擺明架啦"},{"pid":"56ac2f65f1b0a99ae73a63be811415fba07b3e24","tid":1824600,"uid":46431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:29:27.000Z","msg":"智力，性格同埋際遇"},{"pid":"5aec3fe7350dbfd0f0a6f2fb33adaaf05ada8fcc","tid":1824600,"uid":53568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"醒下啦你 公平係攞黎昆人嫁渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你出世有兩隻手兩隻腳 識行識講野 對好多天生殘缺既人已經唔係公平啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係個咁平安既地方長大 對戰亂地方既人已經唔公平啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=